<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>White marble statue base shaft; a stray fragment from the upper right corner of ll.1-7 survives (<measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.315</measure> x <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.205</measure> x <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.11</measure>)</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the face; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>standard second-/third-century forms, <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.03</measure>; diairetic dots flanking Y in l.1, dots for stops in ll.2 and 3, HN in ligature, l.3</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0138" notBefore="0117">117-38 A.D</date> (<rs type="criteria">contests</rs>)
</p>
</div>
